Package org.apache.calcite.linq4j.tree

Class ClassDeclarationFinder

java.lang.Object
org.apache.calcite.linq4j.tree.Shuttle
org.apache.calcite.linq4j.tree.ClassDeclarationFinder
Direct Known Subclasses:
DeterministicCodeOptimizer
public class ClassDeclarationFinder extends Shuttle
Entry point for optimizers that factor out deterministic expressions to final static fields. Instances of this class should not be reused, so new visitor should be created for optimizing a new expression tree.
